"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1919918-paris-2024-olympics-andrew-pozzi-injury-retire\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Team GB hurdler Andrew Pozzi will not compete at the2024 Paris Olympicsafter confirming his unexpected retirement from the sport.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9996431425088864, \"rank\": 0.0003569835419969049, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Pozzi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Pozzi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Pozzi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Pozzi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 32-year-old was called up to participate in the French capital but has been forced to hang up his spikes less than a month out from the Summer Games.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 184, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6528047479816845, \"rank\": 0.4694649554862439, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pozzi - who was crowned world indoor champion in the 60-metre hurdles in Birmingham back in 2018 - had been selected for Great Britain.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham_City_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9981266706858289, \"rank\": 0.0018768452060283383, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham_City_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham_City_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999299689, \"rank\": 6.847493873935015e-11, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, an untimely injury has forced him to make the \\\"profoundly sad\\\" decision.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's with great sadness that I must decline my selection to represent Team GB and announce my withdrawal from the 2024 Olympic Games in Paris,\\\" he wrote onInstagram.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9996431425088864, \"rank\": 0.0003569835419969049, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.163865989068934e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After missing the 2023 season with serious Injury, I have battled exceptionally hard to return to the world stage and earn my place at what would have been my fourth Olympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He went on to confirm his \\\"body gave way in training to another serious ankle fracture\\\" and prompted a round of tests.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pozzi described injury as the \\\"greatest competitor\\\" he'd faced over the course of his 17-year career but said the resilience he'd shown to overcome those setbacks was what he was most proud of.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have decided that now is the right time for me to retire from professional athletics,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is a profoundly sad moment, but also one that I can embrace fully with the knowledge that I have approached every minute of my time in this sport with uncompromising focus, resolute determination and the highest of standards.\\\"\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pozzi made his Olympic bow at London 2012 before going on to compete at both Rio 2016 and Tokyo 2021.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999809006, \"rank\": 1.8050956417354706e-11, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A hamstring injury hampered his performance in his debut on home soil, while he struggled to figure among the medal places at each of his latter two appearances.\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some personal news.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you to everyonepic.twitter.com/cbSxTBFTdh  As fate would have it, Pozzi's personal best in the 110-metre hurdles took place in Paris.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.163865989068934e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He clocked a time of 13.14 seconds in July 2017 and wasn't far off matching that this season, recording a 2024 best of 13.23 seconds in Montgeron earlier this year.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montgeron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Montgeron\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montgeron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montgeron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britain will now be leaning on the talents of Tade Ojora to challenge for silverware in Paris.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2096, \"end\": 2109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999299689, \"rank\": 6.847493873935015e-11, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2190, \"end\": 2195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.163865989068934e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old won gold in the 110m hurdles at each of the 2021, 2022 and 2023 British Athletics Championships before earning selection for his Olympic debut this year.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999968322781719, \"rank\": 3.167732021455504e-06, \"text\": \"British Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Athletics_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Despite beating Pozzi in the past, Ojora's personal best - a wind-assisted 13.16 seconds last year - is just shy of his compatriot's record time.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That being said, he will hope to peak in Paris when the men's event gets underway on August 4.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2801, \"end\": 2806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.163865989068934e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pozzi - who is coached by Malcolm Arnold, former trainer of Olympic silver medallist Colin Jackson - has been denied the glittering farewell from sport he likely always envisioned.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 3036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Arnold\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3250524599389434e-16, \"text\": \"Malcolm Arnold\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Arnold\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Arnold\"}, {\"begin\": 2941, \"end\": 2954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jackson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0395998926847585e-49, \"text\": \"Colin Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, his departure could grant up-and-comer Ojora the opportunity he needs to sparkle later this summer.\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3284, \"end\": 3297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6787581178368535e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3333, \"end\": 3346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6787581178368535e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"